And they run it on Blue Sky, which is pretty cool.

04:47.640 --> 04:50.040
And it's already running obviously on Facebook.

04:51.120 --> 04:53.720
So here's what I want you to do.

04:53.720 --> 04:57.000
I want you to say npm install dash capital D

04:57.000 --> 05:02.000
babel dash plugin dash React dash compiler at beta.

